'''酒精反应'''，又称'''酒精性潮紅反應'''（{{lang-en|Alcohol flush reaction}}）、'''亞洲人潮紅症候群'''，俗称'''上脸'''<ref>{{Cite book|title=上脸|last=现代汉语词典|publisher=商务印书馆|year=|isbn=9787100124508|location=|pages=第1139页|url=http://pic.guoxuedashi.com/xdhycd/1139.gif|access-date=2019-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721141446/http://pic.guoxuedashi.com/xdhycd/1139.gif|archive-date=2019-07-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，是指部分人在饮用[[酒|酒]]類飲料后，在臉部、頸部、肩部以及有時是全身出現的潮紅或是紅色斑塊的情況。[[酒精|酒精]]（乙醇）經攝入後，會受到[[代謝|代謝]]分解而產生[[乙醛|乙醛]]副產品，由於飲者體內[[乙醛脫氫酶|乙醛脫氫酶]]不足，無法迅速將乙醛轉化為[[乙酸|乙酸]]，乙醛因此累積，而造成這種情況。<ref name=":0">{{cite journal|title=The alcohol flushing response: an unrecognized risk factor for esophageal cancer from alcohol consumption|date=March 2009|journal=PLOS Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.1371/journal.pmed.1000050|volume=6|pages=e50|pmc=2659709|pmid=19320537|vauthors=Brooks PJ, Enoch MA, Goldman D, Li TK, Yokoyama A}}</ref>

這種[[症候群|症候群]]會讓飲酒者在酒後感覺不舒服，可能因此較不喜[[酗酒|酗酒]]。<ref name="Yi2010">{{cite journal|title=The ADH1B Arg47His polymorphism in east Asian populations and expansion of rice domestication in history|date=January 2010|journal=BMC Evolutionary Biology|doi=10.1186/1471-2148-10-15|volume=10|pages=15|pmc=2823730|pmid=20089146|vauthors=Peng Y, Shi H, Qi XB, Xiao CJ, Zhong H, Ma RL, Su B}}</ref>然而會有這種症候群的人仍然飲酒，之後與罹患[[食道癌|食道癌]]的風險增加有關聯。<ref name="PLOS2009" /><ref>[http://www.nih.gov/news/health/mar2009/niaaa-23.htm Alcohol Flush Signals Increased Cancer Risk among East Asians] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216062227/http://www.nih.gov/news/health/mar2009/niaaa-23.htm|date=2012-02-16}} March 23, 2009 News Release – [[National_Institutes_of_Health|National Institutes of Health]] (NIH)</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Carcinogenetic impact of ADH1B and ALDH2 genes on squamous cell carcinoma risk of the esophagus with regard to the consumption of alcohol, tobacco and betel quid|first1=Chien-Hung|last2=Lee|first2=Jang-Ming|date=2008|journal=International Journal of Cancer|issue=6|doi=10.1002/ijc.23264|volume=122|pages=1347–56|language=en|issn=1097-0215|pmid=18033686|last3=Wu|first3=Deng-Chyang|last4=Goan|first4=Yih-Gang|last5=Chou|first5=Shah-Hwa|last6=Wu|first6=I.-Chen|last7=Kao|first7=Ein-Long|last8=Chan|first8=Te-Fu|last9=Huang|first9=Meng-Chuan|last1=Lee|first11=Chun-Ying|last11=Lee|first10=Pei-Shih|last10=Chen|doi-access=free}}</ref>

身體發燙的潮紅反應在[[東亞人|東亞人]]中很常見，大約有30%到50%的[[中國人|中國人]]、[[日本人|日本人]]和[[韓國人|韓國人]]在飲酒後會有這種生理反應，包括面部潮紅、[[噁心|噁心]]、[[頭痛|頭痛]]、和[[心跳過速|心跳過速]]。<ref name="Kim2014" /><ref name="J. Yoo 2014 132" /><ref name=":2" />

治疗酗酒药物[[双硫仑|双硫仑]]原理与酒精反应类似，通过降低乙醛脱氢酶的反应，让服药者产生酒精反应并因此不喜酗酒。

==醫學徵象==
[[File:AsianFlushBack.JPG|thumb]]
 
曾經歷過酒精性潮紅反應的人可能不會太容易發生酗酒的情況。[[雙硫侖|雙硫侖]]有時被用於治療酗酒，作用是透過抑制乙醛脫氫酶的作用，導致飲酒者體內的乙醛濃度增加5到10倍。由此產生令人不舒服的潮紅反應，往往會讓人打消再去飲酒的念頭。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/druginfo/medmaster/a682602.html |title=Disulfiram |work=MedlinePlus Drug Information |access-date=15 November 2012 |archive-date=1 October 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081001224410/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/druginfo/medmaster/a682602.html |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{EMedicine|emerg|151|Toxicity, Disulfiram}}</ref>
 
潮紅反應最明顯的症狀是飲酒者的面部和身體泛紅。<ref name=":0" />其他的影響還包括“噁心、頭痛和全身不適”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dujs.dartmouth.edu/fall-2009/esophageal-cancer-and-the-%E2%80%98asian-glow%E2%80%99 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2021-10-07 |archive-date=2016-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112231737/http://dujs.dartmouth.edu/fall-2009/esophageal-cancer-and-the-%e2%80%98asian-glow%e2%80%99 |url-status=live }}</ref>
 
許多{{le|酒精引發呼吸反應|Alcohol-induced respiratory reactions}}，包括[[鼻炎|鼻炎]]，以及[[哮喘|哮喘]]惡化，會在飲酒後1-60分鐘內發生，與導致潮紅反應的原因相同。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Adams KE, Rans TS | title = Adverse reactions to alcohol and alcoholic beverages | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-allergy-asthma-and-immunology_2013-12_111_6/page/439 | journal = Annals of Allergy, Asthma & Immunology | volume = 111 | issue = 6 | pages = 439–45 | date = December 2013 | pmid = 24267355 | doi = 10.1016/j.anai.2013.09.016 }}</ref>

